lternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9611, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 434592, "username": "lynn1su", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lynn1su", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_mini.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_normal.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_large.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xlarge.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xxlarge.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xxxlarge.png?m=1734339081", "created": 1565250257, "last_modified": 1734339081, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Biem", "last_touched": 1774635330, "title": "这种 PUA 的 skill 真的对 ai 有用麻？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1201606", "created": 1774593668, "deleted": 0, "content": "我自己的小龙虾使用了一款 PUA 的 skill 后没有发现变强啊，只会不断重试\r\n模型：GPT-5.4-xhigh\r\n https://i.imgur.com/PsPzyVb.png \r\n https://i.imgur.com/J13WsW5.png \r\n https://i.imgur.com/AR4IWb2.png", "content_rendered": "我自己的小龙虾使用了一款 PUA 的 skill 后没有发现变强啊，只会不断重试<br />模型：GPT-5.4-xhigh<br /> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PsPzyVb.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PsPzyVb.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/J13WsW5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J13WsW5.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/AR4IWb2.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AR4IWb2.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>", "last_modified": 1774593668, "replies": 32, "id": 1201606}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 22830, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3637, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 502926, "username": "Brunuh2Ville2", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Brunuh2Ville2", "website": null, "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a6f6/117d/502926_mini.png?m=1740596558", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a6f6/117d/502926_normal.png?m=1740596558", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a6f6/117d/502926_large.png?m=1740596558", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a6f6/117d/502926_xlarge.png?m=1740596558", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a6f6/117d/502926_xxlarge.png?m=1740596558", "created": 1596867360, "last_modified": 1740596558, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "v2exgo", "last_touched": 1774611964, "title": "国内 AI 开发，受到的冲击没有想象中那么大？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1201575", "created": 1774589282, "deleted": 0, "content": "网络上都在说 claude 和 gpt 最好用，但实际上风控非常严格，在国内使用，很容易封号。\r\n\r\n（各种玄学推测，家宽 ip 设备环境什么就不说了。有的能用，有的封了，原因全靠猜）\r\n\r\n（至于铺天盖地的中转站，挂羊头卖狗肉，模型掺水割韭菜，比比皆是）\r\n\r\n国产模型比如千问、智谱，智力不达标，效果差。提效作用非常有限，还不如自己写。\r\n\r\n换句话说，10 个公司里边，可能都没有一个，能做到 claude 自由 gpt 自由。\r\n\r\n（或者你这么想，公司想用 claude ，先标配个家宽 ip 做梯子，防止被封号。就很抽象吧）\r\n\r\n可能是 2%的人，发出了 92%的音量。\r\n\r\n听到声音的人，全部跟着集体恐慌。\r\n\r\n但现实（国内环境）中的影响，并没有那么大。\r\n\r\n各位如何看？", "content_rendered": "<p>网络上都在说 claude 和 gpt 最好用，但实际上风控非常严格，在国内使用，很容易封号。</p>\n<p>（各种玄学推测，家宽 ip 设备环境什么就不说了。有的能用，有的封了，原因全靠猜）</p>\n<p>（至于铺天盖地的中转站，挂羊头卖狗肉，模型掺水割韭菜，比比皆是）</p>\n<p>国产模型比如千问、智谱，智力不达标，效果差。提效作用非常有限，还不如自己写。</p>\n<p>换句话说，10 个公司里边，可能都没有一个，能做到 claude 自由 gpt 自由。</p>\n<p>（或者你这么想，公司想用 claude ，先标配个家宽 ip 做梯子，防止被封号。就很抽象吧）</p>\n<p>可能是 2%的人，发出了 92%的音量。</p>\n<p>听到声音的人，全部跟着集体恐慌。</p>\n<p>但现实（国内环境）中的影响，并没有那么大。</p>\n<p>各位如何看？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1774590302, "replies": 27, "id": 1201575}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 70310, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9611, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 175675, "username": "Robot2012", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Robot2012", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7ee/86fd/175675_mini.png?m=1774594003", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7ee/86fd/175675_normal.png?m=1774594003", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7ee/86fd/175675_large.png?m=1774594003", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7ee/86fd/175675_xlarge.png?m=1774594003", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7ee/86fd/175675_xxlarge.png?m=1774594003", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7ee/86fd/175675_xxxlarge.png?m=1774594003", "created": 1464849192, "last_modified": 1774594003, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "iorilu", "last_touched": 1774648966, "title": "AI 飞速发展的当下，各大厂们为啥都还在卷 IDE？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1201695", "created": 1774605334, "deleted": 0, "content": "这 IDE 不是一出来就落伍了么？\r\n原本 AI 只能当辅助编程，可 AI 发展太快，强如 Cluade ，完全不需要人来写了，这些 IDE 整出来的意义是啥？", "content_rendered": "<p>这 IDE 不是一出来就落伍了么？\n原本 AI 只能当辅助编程，可 AI 发展太快，强如 Cluade ，完全不需要人来写了，这些 IDE 整出来的意义是啥？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1774605334, "replies": 26, "id": 1201695}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 237853, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4475, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 649071, "username": "techdai", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/techdai", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "北京", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d837/475a/649071_mini.png?m=1774592702", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d837/475a/649071_normal.png?m=1774592702", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d837/475a/649071_large.png?m=1774592702", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d837/475a/649071_xlarge.png?m=1774592702", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d837/475a/649071_xxlarge.png?m=1774592702", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d837/475a/649071_xxxlarge.png?m=1774592702", "created": 1695012093, "last_modified": 1774592702, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "NewYear", "last_touched": 1774626267, "title": "用了豆包输入法，打开新世界，但是有个问题……", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1201576", "created": 1774589322, "deleted": 0, "content": "先说下用下来的几个感受：\r\n\r\n1. 准确率高。我特别多语气词，额、然后、那个之类的，它基本都能过滤掉。数字和英文大部分能准确识别，像微信输入法纠错就一般。\r\n\r\n2. 语音效率高。比之前打字回消息效率高太多了，用过就回不去，特别是临时想到一些东西记下来很方便。\r\n\r\n3. 打字效果一般。不像一直在用的百度输入法打字特别顺畅，联想的词刚好是自己想要的。\r\n\r\n4. 方便练语言组织。我说话完全是没逻辑的，想到啥说啥，用它就相当于练自己的语言组织能力了。\r\n\r\n\r\n问题就是在 iPhone 上面，每次用语音得跳转一下，如果把语音转文字权限设置成一直保持，会不会容易发热耗电？", "content_rendered": "<p>先说下用下来的几个感受：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>准确率高。我特别多语气词，额、然后、那个之类的，它基本都能过滤掉。数字和英文大部分能准确识别，像微信输入法纠错就一般。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>语音效率高。比之前打字回消息效率高太多了，用过就回不去，特别是临时想到一些东西记下来很方便。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>打字效果一般。不像一直在用的百度输入法打字特别顺畅，联想的词刚好是自己想要的。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>方便练语言组织。我说话完全是没逻辑的，想到啥说啥，用它就相当于练自己的语言组织能力了。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>问题就是在 iPhone 上面，每次用语音得跳转一下，如果把语音转文字权限设置成一直保持，会不会容易发热耗电？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1774589322, "replies": 26, "id": 1201576}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 237853, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4475, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 465405, "username": "uCharles", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/uCharles", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c1fc/5c02/465405_mini.png?m=1766416433", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c1fc/5c02/465405_normal.png?m=1766416433", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c1fc/5c02/465405_large.png?m=1766416433", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c1fc/5c02/465405_xlarge.png?m=1766416433", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c1fc/5c02/465405_xxlarge.png?m=1766416433", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c1fc/5c02/465405_xxxlarge.png?m=1766416433", "created": 1579157593, "last_modified": 1766416433, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "saranz", "last_tou